\begin_layout Theorem
A set 
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

 is open if and only if 
\begin_inset Formula $O^{c}$
\end_inset

 is closed.
 Likewise, a set 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 is closed if and only if 
\begin_inset Formula $F^{c}$
\end_inset

 is open.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
